MISTRESS FORD , <ACTION> to Ford</ACTION> How now, sweet Frank? Why art thou melancholy? 

FORD I melancholy? I am not melancholy. Get you home. Go. 

MISTRESS FORD Faith, thou hast some crochets in thy	 head now.—Will you go, Mistress Page? 

MISTRESS PAGE  Have with you.—You’ll come to dinner, George?  <ACTION>Aside to Mistress Ford.</ACTION> Look who comes yonder. 

